{
  "stem": "17526.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Besides, after all what they did to us, how can you-- how can you possibly think of such a thing?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother went to-- my brother went back to Poland in 1974 and I-- I couldn't believe that he really wanted to go back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] finally it started getting to me, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I started to realize I'm getting old and everybody wants-- has a sub human power that draws them to place of his origin, his or her origin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got to realize that it's getting late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1991, I decided I want to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Could you tell us about your-- your visit?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- it was a-- an event that I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not only this, I-- after my first visit, I have a very strong, strong urge to go back again because the things I-- I've left my heart there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- I feel-- I felt much closer to my people while I was there, even though they were not around physically.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I felt much closer spiritually and emotionally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what's urging me to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then also it's getting late in life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who knows, another year or two I may not be able to walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here's what I wrote after coming back from Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the way, I was going to go by myself and my brother did not want me to go out on myself and he joined me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The two of us went to Poland in 1991, at the end of '91.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these are the impressions I've gotten. 'I have just returned from a trip to Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brother, Henry, and I spent seven days in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then we flew to Israel on an El Al from Warsaw to Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
